| No input validation | express-validator on `/users` endpoint |
| Missing security headers | helmet.js middleware |
| No rate limiting | express-rate-limit |
| Exposed errors in production | Conditional error details based on NODE_ENV |
| Request size attacks | 10KB limit on JSON/form data |
| No logging | Request logging middleware |
| Hard-coded config | Environment variables |
| Missing 404 handler | Explicit 404 route |
